Paper: hep-th/9409103

Date: 1994-09-19

Title: Anomaly and Thermodynamics for 2D Spinors in the Aharonov--Bohm Gauge

FieldAuthors: P. Giacconi, F. Maltoni and R. Soldati

Comments: 4 pages, Plain.TeX, Talk given at the Yamada Conference, XXth ICGTMP,

ToyonakaThe axial anomaly is computed for Euclidean Dirac fermions on the plane. Thedependence upon the self-adjoint extensions of the Dirac operator isinvestigated and its relevance concerning the second virial coefficient of theanyon gas is discussed.